extends ../../layout

block content
  h2 Basic controls
  section
    h3 Task 1
    blockquote(cite="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Test_your_skills:_Basic_controls")
      p This task starts you off nice and gently by asking you to create two #[code &lt;input&gt;] elements, for a user's ID and password, along with a submit button.
      ol
        li Create appropriate inputs for user ID and password.
        li You should also associate them with their text labels semantically.
        li Create a submit button inside the remaining list item, with button text of "Log in".
    form
      ul
        li
          label(for="userid") User ID
          input#userid(type="text" name="userid")
        li
          label(for="userpassword") Password
          input#userpassword(type="password" name="password")
        li
          button(type="submit") Log in

  section
    h3 Task 2
    blockquote(cite="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Test_your_skills:_Basic_controls")
      p The next task requires you to create working sets of checkboxes and radio buttons, from the provided text labels.
      ol 
        li Turn the first #[code &lt;fieldset&gt;]'s contents into a set of radio buttons â€” you should only be able to select one pony character at once.
        li Make it so that the first radio button is selected upon page load.
        li Turn the second #[code &lt;fieldset&gt;]'s content into a set of checkboxes.
        li Add a couple more hotdog choices of your own.
    form
      fieldset
        legend
        ul
          li
            label(for="pinkie") Pinkie Pie
            input#pinkie(type="radio", name="pony" checked)
          li
            label(for="rainbow") Rainbow Dash
            input#rainbow(type="radio", name="pony")
          li
            label(for="twilight") Twilight Sparkle
            input#twilight(type="radio", name="pony")
      fieldset
        legend
        ul
          li
            input#vegan(type="checkbox", name="vegan")
            label(for="vegan") Vegan
          li
            input#onions(type="checkbox", name="onions")
            label(for="onions") Onions
          li
            input#mustard(type="checkbox", name="mustard")
            label(for="mustard") Mustard
          li
            input#cheese(type="checkbox", name="cheese")
            label(for="cheese") Cheese
      button(type="submit") Submit
  section
    h3 Task 3
    blockquote(cite="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Forms/Test_your_skills:_Basic_controls")
      p The final task in this set requires you to create a file picker.
      ol
        li Create a basic file picker.
        li Allow the user to pick multiple files at once.
        li Allow the file picker to accept JPG and PNG images only.
    form
      ul
        li
          label(for="gallery-img") Choose gallery images to upload
          input#gallery-img(type="file", accept="image/jpeg,image/png", name="gallery-img", multiple)
  